M48
; Synthetic fixture: METRIC,LZ integer-format coordinates
; Coordinate format: 3 integer + 3 decimal digits (3.3), leading zeros suppressed
; X5000  = LZ pad-left to 6: 005000 -> 005.000 mm = 5.000 mm
; X10000 = LZ pad-left to 6: 010000 -> 010.000 mm = 10.000 mm
FMAT,2
METRIC,LZ
T01C0.800
T02C1.000
%
T01
X5000Y10000
T02
X10000Y5000
M30
